caption.p: Effect of Cuminum cyminum seed essential oil on the differentiation of M. incognita and M. javanica eggs after immersion in test solutions at concentrations of 0, 7.8, 15.6, 31.2, 62.5, 125, 250, and 500 μL/L for 28 days. * Bars with the same color followed by the same letter are not significantly different according to Tukey’s HSD test at p < 0.05.
